* [ ] Is ViewModel using `@StateObject`?
* [ ] Are you replacing full array?
* [ ] Are updates too frequent?
* [ ] Are animations disabled for reload?
* [ ] Are rows Equatable?
* [ ] Using List vs LazyVStack appropriately?

